column2: SELECT b.*, e.bptclass, s.plateid, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.z, s.ra, s.dec, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux_err into mydb.galpair_B1#_sdss_line_radec from mydb.galpair_B1#_sdss as b CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (b.ra_B, b.dec_B, #) as c join DR1#.specObjAll as a on a.bestObjID = c.ObjID join DR1#.galSpecLine AS g on g.specobjid = a.specobjid JOIN DR1#.GalSpecInfo AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid JOIN DR1#.galSpecExtra AS e ON e.specobjid = g.specobjid
